Governance QualityScore as of July 1, 2017 is 4. The pillar scores are Audit: 2; Board: 2; Shareholder Rights: 5; Compensation: 4.Corporate governance scores courtesy of Institutional Shareholder Services (ISS).  Scores indicate decile rank relative to index or region. A decile score of 1 indicates lower governance risk, while a 10 indicates higher governance risk.Yahoo Small BusinessData DisclaimerHelpSuggestionsPrivacyAbout Our AdsTerms (Updated)








